        description:
          `Development Team: Server developer positions are actively recruiting! We support 【Full-time】【Part-time】【Internship】, application link: <a style="color:blue" href="https://ningboesh.feishu.cn/share/base/form/shrcnHtdTPBZGxqwuQgwFAR8LZf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nukkit (Java) Game Development Position Application (Full-time / Part-time / Internship)</a>
